Please use Ctrl + F to find my father's name on this  
list. His name is Ashley Lawson.
This information is accurate for this one year (2008) and my father was a 

member of the BNP coming up to the british elections.
He is no longer a member of the BNP and regrets his actions. This is  
defamation in my opinion as the information has not been taken down after 

the year it was relevant to and the information on here is an obstruction 

to his privacy.
My father's details such as his address, mobile number and email address  
are on here without his consent.
This has caused trouble for him locally to where he lives, I feel that I
do  
not need to provide the address as this site seems to have done so
already.
I implore you to please remove this site even though it seems to be a  
mirror as the high/large majority of people who's names are on this site  
most likely did not give consent for their details to be passed on in such
 
a public fashion.
If this information is not taken down I will be contacting my solicitor as
 
this company is the holder of the site. I have used this company's search 

engine for years as of yet and have recently signed up to it's e-mail  
facility. It is therefore that I will regretfully do this, but my father  
does not need the hassle.
Thank you for the time reading this, if you wish to enquire further, my  
e-mail address is above.

Lee Lawson
